{"tid":752544,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Fuchsia OS 裝置 2021 年推出 或取代 Android 系統","createTime":"2018-07-23T02:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T06:27:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b73f6395e816762fe1493da074953bca68ea5d","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:02:53.000Z","msg":"唐美鳳<br />\n<br />\n在過去兩年 Google 一直在開發新系統 Fuchsia，起初人們以為 Google 只是開發一個概念系統，最近有更多新的消息指 Fuchsia 將會用作取代 Android。Fuchsia 最早在 2016 年於 GitHub 的一些項目的程式碼中出現，系統的最大特色是同時兼容不同大小的屏幕。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了取代 Android 系統，Google 還打算同時取代另一系統 Chrome OS，因為 Fuchsia 不但可以用於智能手機和平板，亦能夠在筆電和智能揚聲器等智能家居產品中預載，屆時 Google 只需專注於一個系統，方便控制之餘，亦易於提供保安更新和進行升級。跟 Android 使用 Linux 作底層不同，Fuchsia 的系統核心 Zircon 是由 Google 基於 Java 自行開發，可以避開 Oracle，令 Google 可以更全面控制平台，例如加入更準確的語音辨識或更多先進的功能。 <br />\nFuchsia 是 Google 一個長遠的計劃，預計 2021 年首播使用 Fuchsia 系統的裝置就會面世。除了要處理技術問題，更重要是要兼顧開發者和硬件生產商。如果計劃順利進行，預算 5 年內就能夠取代 Android 和 Chrome OS。"},{"pid":"aa3b291ed3ca3e4ae0385cc06ea665acf0e88ebe","tid":752544,"uid":58413,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"用Java係咪都係死路一條？"},{"pid":"9bbe56c5f6d0cb6bdeb797596802e2982d6dc1f3","tid":752544,"uid":141060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:09:57.000Z","msg":"2021 食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0b7d508affaafffab52785b984a47c16529465","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"aa3b291ed3ca3e4ae0385cc06ea665acf0e88ebe","tid":752544,"uid":58413,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"用Java係咪都係死路一條？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"Android 系統建基於 Linux 為核心的系統 , 但其需通過核心模擬運行 , 這成了 Android 系統發展最大的致命傷 , 更令應用程式不可以直接的運行 , 成了與 iOS 最大的效果差距 . 開發者都認為 , 如果需要改變這情況 , Android 就需要「砍掉重練」."},{"pid":"87f9cd6cf5b99862635baa9dfbf7441fbd309533","tid":752544,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d0b7d508affaafffab52785b984a47c16529465","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"aa3b291ed3ca3e4ae0385cc06ea665acf0e88ebe","tid":752544,"uid":58413,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"用Java係咪都係死路一條？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"Android 系統建基於 Linux 為核心的系統 , 但其需通過核心模擬運行 , 這成了 Android 系統發展最大的致命傷 , 更令應用程式不可以直接的運行 , 成了與 iOS 最大的效果差距 . 開發者都認為 , 如果需要改變這情況 , Android 就需要「砍掉重練」."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"But java still not native?"},{"pid":"0d1bd209463b18e16d1be566e5d94ef29403debb","tid":752544,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f9cd6cf5b99862635baa9dfbf7441fbd309533","tid":752544,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d0b7d508affaafffab52785b984a47c16529465","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"aa3b291ed3ca3e4ae0385cc06ea665acf0e88ebe","tid":752544,"uid":58413,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"用Java係咪都係死路一條？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"Android 系統建基於 Linux 為核心的系統 , 但其需通過核心模擬運行 , 這成了 Android 系統發展最大的致命傷 , 更令應用程式不可以直接的運行 , 成了與 iOS 最大的效果差距 . 開發者都認為 , 如果需要改變這情況 , Android 就需要「砍掉重練」."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"But java still not native?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"java都唔係最 native,"},{"pid":"08b81769101fe0ac4b363474bb758bbc9a2f4169","tid":752544,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:28:48.000Z","msg":"An做到咁大，係咪真係食得返自己個市埸"},{"pid":"3944b8536f57cc1e1bc5961f0ef7b35c9900fb4b","tid":752544,"uid":35233,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"出左再講"},{"pid":"14826f17058c98f187d41808e2600a9f198d1f5b","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59f775104ef67835b5441d263cf86e7ece22ef3","tid":752544,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"又傳？<br />\n上次咪話係假新聞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09aa089dbf243d0f59e48e7adf250838026b54a1","tid":752544,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59f775104ef67835b5441d263cf86e7ece22ef3","tid":752544,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"又傳？<br />\n上次咪話係假新聞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"未必家用   應該商用物聯網  可以一個平台統一"},{"pid":"66ee16a28fa48f9c664b2c04ed50e9b83cda82bb","tid":752544,"uid":35542,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"寫文果個資料錯晒亂咁寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle澄清話無5年計劃<br />\n不過我估遲早都會取代Android/Chrome OS<br />\n<br />\nFuchsia係capability-based OS<br />\nZircon係microkernel,用C++寫,無Java<br />\nFuchsia分咗4層,Zircon, Garnet, Peridot, Topaz<br />\n寫app可以用Dart/Flutter,或者FIDL,暫時支援C, C++, Dart, Go, Rust<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fuchsia.googlesource.com/docs/+/HEAD/the-book/README.md\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffuchsia.googlesource.com%2Fdocs%2F%2B%2FHEAD%2Fthe-book%2FREADME.md&d=7zgpRuyat%2F7NDD5N4EVKjJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=68c9acc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://fuchsia.googlesource.com/docs/+/HEAD/the-book/README.md</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://fuchsia.googlesource.com/docs/+/HEAD/glossary.md\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffuchsia.googlesource.com%2Fdocs%2F%2B%2FHEAD%2Fglossary.md&d=7zgpRuyat%2F7NDD5N4EVKjJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c7085324\" target=\"_blank\">https://fuchsia.googlesource.com/docs/+/HEAD/glossary.md</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://fuchsia-review.googlesource.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffuchsia-review.googlesource.com&d=7zgpRuyat%2F7NDD5N4EVKjJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=fde13f58\" target=\"_blank\">https://fuchsia-review.googlesource.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://9to5google.com/guides/fuchsia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F9to5google.com%2Fguides%2Ffuchsia%2F&d=7zgpRuyat%2F7NDD5N4EVKjJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0833fef4\" target=\"_blank\">https://9to5google.com/guides/fuchsia/</a>"},{"pid":"51b6a7910d08081cd30e462b9d7fa085e5c88a50","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"Google 回應更多 Fuchsia OS的細節，可惜在 5 年內仍然取代不了 Android<br />\n 2018-07-23 <a href=\"http://TechApple.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTechApple.com&d=7zgpRuyat%2F7NDD5N4EVKjJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e0f0dd8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">TechApple.com</a> 編輯部<br />\n也許 Google 的 Fuchsia OS 已經不是什麼秘密（在 GitHub 上面就有一大堆 Repo) ，但它的細節仍然相當神秘，據知 Google 投入超過 100 名工程師於其中，當中甚至包括 Material Design 的設計師 Matias Duarte ，可以想像這是一個相當龐大的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n在 Bloomberg 早前的訪問中，他們公佈了更多的細節：Fuchsia OS 目標是可以在各種大小屏幕的裝置上面運行，甚至取代現時 Google 旗下的 OS ，但隨後又回應 CNET :「要取代 Android ？5 年內我們也沒有這樣的計劃！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以肯定的是 Fuchsia 不會像 Android 一樣只支援手機或者 Tablets ，連基本的設計也會不一樣，畢竟第一個目標是可以支援多樣性的裝置，最少也會像網站一樣擁有多變性吧，同時他們亦考慮到 IoT 這個潮流，所以 Fuchsia 有機會成為家用 IoT 終端，並擁有比現時更多的語言控制終於。<br />\n<br />\n更重要的是 Fuchsia 開發人員已經表示不會像 Android 一樣使用 Linux Kernel ，其中一個目的為了避免與 Oracle 有任何的連繫（畢竟他們的一個眼中釘就是 JAVA，卻避免不了）。他們指出整個系統都是一個開源的實驗，是對於創新的投資。<br />\n<br />\n談到程式語言，主流的 Android 開發者仍然是使用 JAVA 、Kotlin 這兩種程式語言，但從現時流出的資料來說， Fuchsia OS 將支援 C++、Python、Go 、RUST 甚至 Swift 等多種編程語言，可以見到這系統比起 Android 的想法成熟得多，可惜要取代 Android 或是 Chrome OS 並不會在 5 年內發生，最少這不是 Google 現時的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n嗯，Android 開發者還是繼續與 Container 和大大小小的屏幕再博鬥一陣子吧（笑）。"},{"pid":"4ed5584789a456c83cf4aeec522aa6f3098841df","tid":752544,"uid":30006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"其實真係要黎一個當年 WIN95 咁樣全部一刀切換新先有希望<br />\n<br />\n成個kernel 轉先可以提升效能<br />\n<br />\n不過全部app要重寫我估google未必敢take risk，除非真係好似當年Win98咁玩晒八成巿場先會敢轉<br />\n<br />\niPhone 仲係大賣佢地應該都唔敢郁"},{"pid":"a69b0fa68bb8dc8dc7af1f54eedf4ded034f061c","tid":752544,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"如果今次google 成功，最慘嘅唔係apple, 係Microsoft"},{"pid":"8e7568219b99d6f3134c1371b4b01e81e0ad0fb3","tid":752544,"uid":146427,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"Google 間接承認Android 唔掂<br />\n<br />\n叫班An9 情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f631593d84b54b8f41aa6e3ec023a5bbf86baa3","tid":752544,"uid":14548,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"iPhone 末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔用android主要原因真係因爲佢冇咁順(唔好同我講android宜家已經好順呢d廢話)"},{"pid":"fd2b9121139d90ed59435fbf99a1c2420fb7e2df","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa90dafc06a3bb2ac292d0dbf17d514e3a48a86","tid":752544,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f631593d84b54b8f41aa6e3ec023a5bbf86baa3","tid":752544,"uid":14548,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"iPhone 末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔用android主要原因真係因爲佢冇咁順(唔好同我講android宜家已經好順呢d廢話)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:02:26.000Z","msg":"Apple已經好成功咁建立左個eco-system<br />\n應該好難會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feab03a6a19c335b2fbd6893507a6bab797b25c9","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0385e59d73e44e302678ecbc18890668839d174","tid":752544,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446f1a4f7d657af56ef32b484e6f1158107ac966","tid":752544,"uid":1552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f631593d84b54b8f41aa6e3ec023a5bbf86baa3","tid":752544,"uid":14548,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"iPhone 末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔用android主要原因真係因爲佢冇咁順(唔好同我講android宜家已經好順呢d廢話)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"出左先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Google啲嘢隨時變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d6f4256c473df3d2c7cf898868b9acd9e68c11","tid":752544,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ed5584789a456c83cf4aeec522aa6f3098841df","tid":752544,"uid":30006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"其實真係要黎一個當年 WIN95 咁樣全部一刀切換新先有希望<br />\n<br />\n成個kernel 轉先可以提升效能<br />\n<br />\n不過全部app要重寫我估google未必敢take risk，除非真係好似當年Win98咁玩晒八成巿場先會敢轉<br />\n<br />\niPhone 仲係大賣佢地應該都唔敢郁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"Windows 95 只不過係收埋個 DOS 同自己 Load Windows (以前 D 機自己係 autoexec.bat 到加 Windows), 到 98, ME 都仍然係舊 Windows.  當年其實 NT 已經好先進, 但係無咩人會裝因為打 DOS Game 唔方便.  <br />\n<br />\n去到 XP 先真正用 NT 底, 但都唔係砍掉重鍊.  (XP = Windows 2000 既家用版)<br />\n<br />\nAndroid 一早過 8 成, 只不過賺得唔夠蘋果多.  佢要寫過新姐係要用模擬 Mode 行 Android d APK.  亦即係要 CPU 再次大躍進先頂到. <br />\n<br />\nAndroid 既失敗亦係因為 Android 太成功.  Palm - Pocket PC - iOS - Android.  <br />\n每一間公司都衰係自己既成功上面.  <br />\n<br />\n如果呢刻 Amazon 出自己 OS 再 Open Source 就有機會打低 Android. <br />\n否則真係睇唔出呢個世界有任何一間公司會花錢落去呢個氹到."},{"pid":"4d71494e0a7b024103ee7efa973c59138365d327","tid":752544,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"Google最興攪攪下唔攪 雷聲大雨點小<br />\n估唔到Chorme OS咁快死"},{"pid":"11f41ce387ae2799c2e80d709fcfe34a1668e804","tid":752544,"uid":686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"446f1a4f7d657af56ef32b484e6f1158107ac966","tid":752544,"uid":1552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f631593d84b54b8f41aa6e3ec023a5bbf86baa3","tid":752544,"uid":14548,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"iPhone 末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔用android主要原因真係因爲佢冇咁順(唔好同我講android宜家已經好順呢d廢話)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"出左先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Google啲嘢隨時變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:14:47.000Z","msg":"dead before birth <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}